Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the fruit basket!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Warriors of the Sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends, we attack together!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.06,0:00:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I overestimated myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re welcome;
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,protecting everyone is our duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to be heroes, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie’s in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s the matter, Tibbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I accidentally broke a cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the radar,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,a fragment is somewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.22,0:01:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s work hard together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait;
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,why are you three dressed up like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:01:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh… Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s split up and go search for the fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,we must discreetly ensure the safety
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of Tibbie and Jonie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Warriors of the Sea, let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie, Weslie,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,have you noticed any danger on your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re safe for now; no sign of danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How about your side, Paddi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Start up, Morning Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, Tibbie is currently in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t hurt Ti—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was just a little fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s air spewing everywhere;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,how am I supposed to get through?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not every hole is spewing air;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,watch me find a safe path!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re amazing, Paddi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t count on it spewing oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hero’s Pike!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hero’s Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Seaweed Baozi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Their gadgets are so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally know why we can’t be heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know why, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s because
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s because our gadgets aren’t big enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, our submarines have both offense and defense;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,incredibly powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We Warriors of the Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Tibbie and Jonie went.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Could they be inside the cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let’s hurry inside and check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it’s their submarines!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie and Jonie are in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It took Tibbie and Jonie away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are there so many?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll distract them;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you two go after Tibbie and Jonie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The armor is too heavy;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunderbolt can’t accelerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,could you please take off my armor quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot I’d changed Morning Sun’s mechanic abilities
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to destructive abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, they’re already gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi, activate search mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I removed the search antenna
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to add new gadgets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s all our fault for being impulsive
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and causing Tibbie and Jonie to get kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t want to be a “hero!”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want Jonie and Tibbie to come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you guys for saving me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to thank us;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it’s what we’re supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When I grow up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to become a hero like you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you have a desire to protect others,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you, too, can be a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to protect our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We Warriors of the Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,here we go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is another one of the devil rays’ caves;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie and Jonie are right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let’s hurry up and get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Any more delays,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and Tibbie and Jonie will be in even more danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceed as planned;
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll distract them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you two go and carry out the rescue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they mean by that gurgling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll translate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, they don’t understand what you’re saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,“Gurgle, gurgle!”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say to make them so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that one of their friends is in your submarine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s hurry inside and search!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way do we go now, Paddi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s too much interference here;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t search!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let’s split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi and Sparky should be doing well by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to hurry back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re already caught up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything, Paddi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this place is too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get back so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t mean to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,U-turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie! Jonie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re here to rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you guys misunderstood the devil rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole thing is a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was helping a devil ray
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,extract a fragment that was stuck in its teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fragment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did the devil rays take you guys away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably thought that we were in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil rays have warmly welcomed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But due to the language barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we couldn’t leave when we wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was our fault all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If only they could understand me talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,translate the situation to the devil rays!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,“Gurgle, gurgle!”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve brought snacks for you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:12:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you have a desire to protect others,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you, too, can be a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it’s not that easy to be a hero after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So the reason you guys did all that stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,was because you wanted to be heroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We might not be able to become the kind of heroes that they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as you do the best that you can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you’re a hero, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, come have some snacks, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave some for me, Paddi!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
